    "help_hero": {
      "type": "ss-simple-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "q1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do I upload my prescription?",
            "answer": "<p>After adding frames to your cart, you'll be prompted to enter your prescription details at checkout. You can type in your prescription manually or upload a photo of your prescription card. Our optical team reviews every prescription before dispatching your order. If you're unsure about any values (SPH, CYL, AXIS, ADD), contact us at hello@glassessiam.com and we'll help you.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q2": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What lens types do you offer?",
            "answer": "<p>We offer a full range of lenses to suit every need:</p><ul><li><strong>Single Vision</strong> — from ฿690. For distance or reading correction.</li><li><strong>Progressive (No-line Bifocal)</strong> — from ฿2,490. Distance, intermediate and near in one lens.</li><li><strong>Blue Light Blocking</strong> — from ฿1,290. Reduces digital eye strain from screens.</li><li><strong>Polarized</strong> — from ฿1,190. Eliminates glare for driving and outdoors.</li><li><strong>Transitions®</strong> — from ฿2,990. Automatically darken in sunlight.</li></ul><p>Visit our <a href='/pages/lenses'>Lenses page</a> for full details on all options.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you offer free shipping?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes — free standard shipping on all orders throughout Thailand. Orders are typically dispatched within 1–2 business days after your prescription is verified. Delivery usually takes 2–5 business days depending on your location. Express shipping is available at checkout for an additional fee.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q4": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What is your returns policy?",
            "answer": "<p>We offer a 30-day return policy on all unworn frames in their original condition and packaging. If your frames arrive damaged or there's an issue with your lenses, we'll replace them free of charge. To start a return, email hello@glassessiam.com with your order number and we'll guide you through the process.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q5": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How does the virtual try-on work?",
            "answer": "<p>Our virtual try-on feature uses your device's camera to show you how any frame looks on your face in real time. Simply click the 'Try On' button on any product page or collection page. No app download is needed — it works directly in your browser. Once the try-on is open, you'll see an 'Add to Cart' panel so you can buy immediately.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q6": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What payment methods do you accept?",
            "answer": "<p>We accept all major payment methods including:</p><ul><li>Credit & debit cards (Visa, Mastercard, Amex)</li><li>QR PromptPay</li><li>Bank transfer</li><li>Instalment plans (0% interest available on selected cards)</li></ul><p>All payments are processed securely. We never store your card details.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q7": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Can I get glasses without a prescription?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes! We sell many frames as non-prescription (plano) glasses, reading glasses, and fashion frames. You can also order prescription sunglasses. Simply select 'No prescription' or 'Plano lenses' during the checkout lens selection step.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q8": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do I find my frame size?",
            "answer": "<p>Frame size is printed on the inside of most frames and typically looks like: <strong>52-18-140</strong> (lens width - bridge width - temple length, all in mm). You can also use our virtual try-on to see how different frame sizes look on your face. If you need help choosing, email us a photo and we'll recommend the right size for your face shape.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q9": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How long does it take to receive my order?",
            "answer": "<p>Once your prescription is verified (usually within 1 business day), your lenses are cut and fitted in our optical lab. Total turnaround time is typically:</p><ul><li><strong>Single Vision:</strong> 3–5 business days</li><li><strong>Progressive:</strong> 5–7 business days</li><li><strong>Frames only (no prescription):</strong> 1–3 business days</li></ul><p>You'll receive a tracking number by email as soon as your order ships.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q10": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Are your branded frames genuine?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes — 100%. All Ray-Ban, Oakley, Carolina Herrera, and other branded frames sold on GlassesSiam are genuine, authorised products. We source directly from authorised distributors and every frame comes with its original case, cleaning cloth, and manufacturer warranty.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q11": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "I need help — how do I contact you?",
            "answer": "<p>We're always happy to help! You can reach us by:</p><ul><li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href='mailto:hello@glassessiam.com'>hello@glassessiam.com</a> — we reply within 24 hours</li><li><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href='tel:+6620016789'>+66 2 001 6789</a> — Mon–Sat, 9am–6pm (Bangkok time)</li><li><strong>Contact form:</strong> <a href='/pages/contact'>Visit our Contact page</a></li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
